room_title: Escape room "Matter of Time" by Exit Plan in Washington, D.C.
room_address: 201 Royal SE Suite F Leesburg, VA 20175
room_description: Is the clock ticking or has it stopped completely? The future needs to be altered, but only by meddling with the past. The delicate balance of a dimension-spanning two-time streams is in your hands. One small mistake could alter the very future of your own existence. Choose your actions wisely, it's only a matter of time.
